<br />
You MUST keep going.  When I first started reading this story I did not give you much of a chance to keep my attention past your first post, but I was dead wrong.  I feel like I am addicted to a very good book, but I must beg for more pages from the author.  This is quite a strange feeling.  When I have had it in the past, I finished the book that night.  I must be honest and tell you that I am fearful that I will be left hanging.  Do not let that come to fruition.<br />
